overview: We always make it a point to give our freshmen a warm welcome here at CF and in this second volume of our Fresh-Faced Freshman we're happy to present Jack, Brody, Skye, and Scott in four more of our hottest jock-on-twink scenes. These boys really come out of their shells when our hunky upperclassmen put them through their special paces! Our young inexperienced freshmen are fast learners when it comes to taking big cocks in every position imaginable and they're eager to show you that they can keep up just as well as our veterans.
title: Fresh-Faced Freshmen 2
